'''Azwil''' d azamul (eg: "3", "7", "13") imettel yiwen uzal ameḍnaw (valeur numérique), yettuseqdac i tagensest (représentation) n [[Amḍan|yimḍanen]] (nombres).

Amgirred ger azwil d umḍan am amgirred ger wawal d [[Asekkil|usekkil]] eg: 

*"allelluc n gma", yesɛa 3 awalen: "allelluc", "n" , "gma". Awal amezwaru yesɛa 8 isekkilen, wis sin yesɛa 1 kan.
*"7820" d amḍan yesɛa 4 izwilen, "5" d amḍan yesɛa 1 wezwil kan.

Llan 10 izwilen: 0 (ILem) - 1 (Yiwen) - 2 (Sin) - 3 (Kraḍ) - 4 (Kuẓ) - 5 (Sem) - 6 (Sed) - 7 (Sa) - 8 (Tam)- 9 (Tẓa)

Izwilen i nesseqdac d izwilen [[Turuft|urufiyen]], yekka-d aẓar-nsen seg izwilen [[Ihendiye]], [[Aɛraben]] mazal ar tura sseqdacen izwilen ihendiyen. 

